newProducts.title: Claude Code
newProducts.description: Anthropic's new AI-powered coding assistant and IDE that integrates Claude's capabilities directly into development workflows. Features include code generation, debugging, project understanding, and multi-file editing capabilities.

newProducts.title: Aider
newProducts.description: AI pair programming tool that works in your terminal. Enables AI to edit files in your local git repository with multi-file editing, project context awareness, and git integration.

newProducts.title: Supermaven
newProducts.description: Fast AI code completion tool that claims to be significantly faster than alternatives. Integrates with popular IDEs and supports multiple programming languages.

newProducts.title: Codeium Chat
newProducts.description: Enhanced chat interface from Codeium that provides conversational coding assistance with project context awareness and multi-file understanding.

newProducts.title: Windsurf
newProducts.description: New IDE from Codeium that combines AI assistance with traditional development features, focusing on seamless AI-human collaboration workflows.

newProducts.title: Morph IDE
newProducts.description: AI-native IDE that automatically adapts to your coding patterns and project structure. Features proactive code suggestions and automated refactoring.

newProducts.title: FSD.dev
newProducts.description: Full-stack development platform that uses AI to generate complete applications from natural language descriptions, including frontend, backend, and database design.

newProducts.title: Replit Agent v2
newProducts.description: Enhanced version of Replit's AI agent with improved code generation, debugging capabilities, and better understanding of complex project structures.

newProducts.title: OpenAI Code Interpreter API
newProducts.description: API version of OpenAI's code execution capabilities that allows developers to integrate code interpretation and execution into their applications.

newProducts.title: DevOps GPT
newProducts.description: AI-powered DevOps assistant that automates infrastructure setup, CI/CD pipeline creation, and deployment configurations based on natural language input.

newProducts.title: K3y
newProducts.description: AI-powered debugging assistant that analyzes error logs, stack traces, and code to provide intelligent solutions and root cause analysis.

newProducts.title: Act
newProducts.description: Open-source framework for building autonomous AI agents that can perform software development tasks, including code generation, testing, and deployment.
